meanings: 칭찬 You are a walking encyclopedia.
칭찬 You seem to know everything.
실용회화-칭찬 You must be a human encyclopedia.
(알지 못하다) do not know, (이해하지 못하다) do not understand
(경험이 없다) have no experience, be ignorant of

meanings.meaning: what the eye doesn't see (the heart doesn't grieve over)

vlive.korean: 덕질에 대해서라면 모르는 게 없는 엄청난 척척 박사야! He's the smartest! He knows everything. 듣기 View video V CREW : [V CREW] 로디 어나운스‼️ - 여러분 로ㅡ하! 신입 스트리머 인사드립니다!👀 (feat. 💩손)
